{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I love the Internet."},{"time":3000,"text":"It's true."},{"time":5000,"text":"Think about everything it has brought us."},{"time":7000,"text":"Think about all the services we use,"},{"time":10000,"text":"all the connectivity,"},{"time":12000,"text":"all the entertainment,"},{"time":14000,"text":"all the business, all the commerce."},{"time":17000,"text":"And it's happening during our lifetimes."},{"time":20000,"text":"I'm pretty sure that one day"},{"time":23000,"text":"we'll be writing history books"},{"time":25000,"text":"hundreds of years from now. This time"},{"time":28000,"text":"our generation will be remembered"},{"time":31000,"text":"as the generation that got online,"},{"time":34000,"text":"the generation"},{"time":36000,"text":"that built something really and truly global."},{"time":39000,"text":"But yes, it's also true"},{"time":42000,"text":"that the Internet has problems, very serious problems,"},{"time":45000,"text":"problems with security"},{"time":48000,"text":"and problems with privacy."},{"time":51000,"text":"I've spent my career"},{"time":53000,"text":"fighting these problems."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56000,"text":"So let me show you something."},{"time":60000,"text":"This here"},{"time":62000,"text":"is Brain."},{"time":64000,"text":"This is a floppy disk"},{"time":66000,"text":"-- five and a quarter-inch floppy disk"},{"time":68000,"text":"infected by Brain.A."},{"time":70000,"text":"It's the first virus we ever found"},{"time":72000,"text":"for PC computers."},{"time":75000,"text":"And we actually know"},{"time":77000,"text":"where Brain came from."},{"time":79000,"text":"We know because it says so"},{"time":81000,"text":"inside the code."},{"time":83000,"text":"Let's take a look."},{"time":90000,"text":"All right."},{"time":93000,"text":"That's the boot sector of an infected floppy,"},{"time":96000,"text":"and if we take a closer look inside,"},{"time":99000,"text":"we'll see that right there,"},{"time":101000,"text":"it says, \"Welcome to the dungeon.\""},{"time":105000,"text":"And then it continues,"},{"time":107000,"text":"saying, 1986, Basit and Amjad."},{"time":110000,"text":"And Basit and Amjad are first names,"},{"time":113000,"text":"Pakistani first names."},{"time":115000,"text":"In fact, there's a phone number and an address in Pakistan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":118000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":123000,"text":"Now, 1986."},{"time":126000,"text":"Now it's 2011."},{"time":128000,"text":"That's 25 years ago."},{"time":130000,"text":"The PC virus problem is 25 years old now."},{"time":134000,"text":"So half a year ago,"},{"time":136000,"text":"I decided to go to Pakistan myself."},{"time":139000,"text":"So let's see, here's a couple of photos I took while I was in Pakistan."},{"time":142000,"text":"This is from the city of Lahore,"},{"time":144000,"text":"which is around 300 kilometers south"},{"time":146000,"text":"from Abbottabad, where Bin Laden was caught."},{"time":149000,"text":"Here's a typical street view."},{"time":152000,"text":"And here's the street or road leading to this building,"},{"time":155000,"text":"which is 730 Nizam block at Allama Iqbal Town."},{"time":159000,"text":"And I knocked on the door."},{"time":161000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":163000,"text":"You want to guess who opened the door?"},{"time":165000,"text":"Basit and Amjad; they are still there."},{"time":167000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":169000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":173000,"text":"So here standing up is Basit."},{"time":176000,"text":"Sitting down is his brother Amjad."},{"time":179000,"text":"These are the guys who wrote the first PC virus."},{"time":182000,"text":"Now of course, we had a very interesting discussion."},{"time":185000,"text":"I asked them why."},{"time":187000,"text":"I asked them how they feel about what they started."},{"time":190000,"text":"And I got some sort of satisfaction"},{"time":193000,"text":"from learning that both Basit and Amjad"},{"time":196000,"text":"had had their computers infected dozens of times"},{"time":199000,"text":"by completely unrelated other viruses"},{"time":201000,"text":"over these years."},{"time":203000,"text":"So there is some sort of justice"},{"time":205000,"text":"in the world after all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":209000,"text":"Now, the viruses that we used to see"},{"time":211000,"text":"in the 1980s and 1990s"},{"time":213000,"text":"obviously are not a problem any more."},{"time":216000,"text":"So let me just show you a couple of examples"},{"time":218000,"text":"of what they used to look like."},{"time":220000,"text":"What I'm running here"},{"time":222000,"text":"is a system that enables me"},{"time":224000,"text":"to run age-old programs on a modern computer."},{"time":227000,"text":"So let me just mount some drives. Go over there."},{"time":230000,"text":"What we have here is a list of old viruses."},{"time":233000,"text":"So let me just run some viruses on my computer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":236000,"text":"For example,"},{"time":238000,"text":"let's go with the Centipede virus first."},{"time":240000,"text":"And you can see at the top of the screen,"},{"time":242000,"text":"there's a centipede scrolling across your computer"},{"time":244000,"text":"when you get infected by this one."},{"time":246000,"text":"You know that you're infected"},{"time":248000,"text":"because it actually shows up."},{"time":250000,"text":"Here's another one. This is the virus called Crash,"},{"time":253000,"text":"invented in Russia in 1992."},{"time":255000,"text":"Let me show you one which actually makes some sound."},{"time":259000,"text":"(Siren noise)"},{"time":265000,"text":"And the last example,"},{"time":267000,"text":"guess what the Walker virus does?"},{"time":269000,"text":"Yes, there's a guy walking across your screen"},{"time":271000,"text":"once you get infected."},{"time":273000,"text":"So it used to be fairly easy to know"},{"time":276000,"text":"that you're infected by a virus,"},{"time":279000,"text":"when the viruses were written by hobbyists"},{"time":281000,"text":"and teenagers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":283000,"text":"Today, they are no longer being written"},{"time":285000,"text":"by hobbyists and teenagers."},{"time":287000,"text":"Today, viruses are a global problem."},{"time":290000,"text":"What we have here in the background"},{"time":292000,"text":"is an example of our systems that we run in our labs,"},{"time":295000,"text":"where we track virus infections worldwide."},{"time":297000,"text":"So we can actually see in real time"},{"time":299000,"text":"that we've just blocked viruses in Sweden and Taiwan"},{"time":302000,"text":"and Russia and elsewhere."},{"time":304000,"text":"In fact, if I just connect back to our lab systems"},{"time":307000,"text":"through the Web,"},{"time":309000,"text":"we can see in real time"},{"time":311000,"text":"just some kind of idea of how many viruses,"},{"time":314000,"text":"how many new examples of malware we find every single day."},{"time":317000,"text":"Here's the latest virus we've found,"},{"time":319000,"text":"in a file called Server.exe."},{"time":321000,"text":"And we found it right over here three seconds ago --"},{"time":324000,"text":"the previous one, six seconds ago."},{"time":326000,"text":"And if we just scroll around,"},{"time":329000,"text":"it's just massive."},{"time":331000,"text":"We find tens of thousands, even hundreds of thousands."},{"time":334000,"text":"And that's the last 20 minutes of malware"},{"time":337000,"text":"every single day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":339000,"text":"So where are all these coming from then?"},{"time":342000,"text":"Well today, it's the organized criminal gangs"},{"time":346000,"text":"writing these viruses"},{"time":348000,"text":"because they make money with their viruses."},{"time":350000,"text":"It's gangs like --"},{"time":352000,"text":"let's go to GangstaBucks.com."},{"time":355000,"text":"This is a website operating in Moscow"},{"time":358000,"text":"where these guys are buying infected computers."},{"time":362000,"text":"So if you are a virus writer"},{"time":364000,"text":"and you're capable of infecting Windows computers,"},{"time":366000,"text":"but you don't know what to do with them,"},{"time":368000,"text":"you can sell those infected computers --"},{"time":370000,"text":"somebody else's computers -- to these guys."},{"time":372000,"text":"And they'll actually pay you money for those computers."},{"time":376000,"text":"So how do these guys then monetize"},{"time":379000,"text":"those infected computers?"},{"time":381000,"text":"Well there's multiple different ways,"},{"time":383000,"text":"such as banking trojans, which will steal money from your online banking accounts"},{"time":386000,"text":"when you do online banking,"},{"time":389000,"text":"or keyloggers."},{"time":392000,"text":"Keyloggers silently sit on your computer, hidden from view,"},{"time":396000,"text":"and they record everything you type."},{"time":399000,"text":"So you're sitting on your computer and you're doing Google searches."},{"time":402000,"text":"Every single Google search you type"},{"time":404000,"text":"is saved and sent to the criminals."},{"time":407000,"text":"Every single email you write is saved and sent to the criminals."},{"time":410000,"text":"Same thing with every single password and so on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":414000,"text":"But the thing that they're actually looking for most"},{"time":416000,"text":"are sessions where you go online"},{"time":418000,"text":"and do online purchases in any online store."},{"time":421000,"text":"Because when you do purchases in online stores,"},{"time":423000,"text":"you will be typing in your name, the delivery address,"},{"time":426000,"text":"your credit card number and the credit card security codes."},{"time":429000,"text":"And here's an example of a file"},{"time":431000,"text":"we found from a server a couple of weeks ago."},{"time":433000,"text":"That's the credit card number,"},{"time":435000,"text":"that's the expiration date, that's the security code,"},{"time":437000,"text":"and that's the name of the owner of the card."},{"time":439000,"text":"Once you gain access to other people's credit card information,"},{"time":442000,"text":"you can just go online and buy whatever you want"},{"time":444000,"text":"with this information."},{"time":447000,"text":"And that, obviously, is a problem."},{"time":449000,"text":"We now have a whole underground marketplace"},{"time":453000,"text":"and business ecosystem"},{"time":456000,"text":"built around online crime."}]},{"cues":[{"time":459000,"text":"One example of how these guys"},{"time":461000,"text":"actually are capable of monetizing their operations:"},{"time":464000,"text":"we go and have a look at the pages of INTERPOL"},{"time":467000,"text":"and search for wanted persons."},{"time":469000,"text":"We find guys like Bjorn Sundin, originally from Sweden,"},{"time":472000,"text":"and his partner in crime,"},{"time":474000,"text":"also listed on the INTERPOL wanted pages,"},{"time":476000,"text":"Mr. Shaileshkumar Jain,"},{"time":478000,"text":"a U.S. citizen."},{"time":480000,"text":"These guys were running an operation called I.M.U.,"},{"time":483000,"text":"a cybercrime operation through which they netted millions."},{"time":486000,"text":"They are both right now on the run."},{"time":489000,"text":"Nobody knows where they are."},{"time":491000,"text":"U.S. officials, just a couple of weeks ago,"},{"time":493000,"text":"froze a Swiss bank account"},{"time":495000,"text":"belonging to Mr. Jain,"},{"time":497000,"text":"and that bank account had 14.9 million U.S. dollars on it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":501000,"text":"So the amount of money online crime generates"},{"time":504000,"text":"is significant."},{"time":506000,"text":"And that means that the online criminals"},{"time":508000,"text":"can actually afford to invest into their attacks."},{"time":511000,"text":"We know that online criminals"},{"time":513000,"text":"are hiring programmers, hiring testing people,"},{"time":516000,"text":"testing their code,"},{"time":518000,"text":"having back-end systems with SQL databases."},{"time":521000,"text":"And they can afford to watch how we work --"},{"time":524000,"text":"like how security people work --"},{"time":526000,"text":"and try to work their way around"},{"time":528000,"text":"any security precautions we can build."},{"time":530000,"text":"They also use the global nature of Internet"},{"time":533000,"text":"to their advantage."},{"time":535000,"text":"I mean, the Internet is international."},{"time":537000,"text":"That's why we call it the Internet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":539000,"text":"And if you just go and take a look"},{"time":541000,"text":"at what's happening in the online world,"},{"time":544000,"text":"here's a video built by Clarified Networks,"},{"time":546000,"text":"which illustrates how one single malware family is able to move around the world."},{"time":550000,"text":"This operation, believed to be originally from Estonia,"},{"time":553000,"text":"moves around from one country to another"},{"time":555000,"text":"as soon as the website is tried to shut down."},{"time":557000,"text":"So you just can't shut these guys down."},{"time":560000,"text":"They will switch from one country to another,"},{"time":562000,"text":"from one jurisdiction to another --"},{"time":564000,"text":"moving around the world,"},{"time":566000,"text":"using the fact that we don't have the capability"},{"time":568000,"text":"to globally police operations like this."},{"time":571000,"text":"So the Internet is as if"},{"time":573000,"text":"someone would have given free plane tickets"},{"time":575000,"text":"to all the online criminals of the world."},{"time":578000,"text":"Now, criminals who weren't capable of reaching us before"},{"time":581000,"text":"can reach us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":583000,"text":"So how do you actually go around finding online criminals?"},{"time":586000,"text":"How do you actually track them down?"},{"time":588000,"text":"Let me give you an example."},{"time":590000,"text":"What we have here is one exploit file."},{"time":593000,"text":"Here, I'm looking at the Hex dump of an image file,"},{"time":597000,"text":"which contains an exploit."},{"time":599000,"text":"And that basically means, if you're trying to view this image file on your Windows computer,"},{"time":602000,"text":"it actually takes over your computer and runs code."}]},{"cues":[{"time":605000,"text":"Now, if you'll take a look at this image file --"},{"time":608000,"text":"well there's the image header,"},{"time":610000,"text":"and there the actual code of the attack starts."},{"time":613000,"text":"And that code has been encrypted,"},{"time":615000,"text":"so let's decrypt it."},{"time":617000,"text":"It has been encrypted with XOR function 97."},{"time":619000,"text":"You just have to believe me,"},{"time":621000,"text":"it is, it is."},{"time":623000,"text":"And we can go here"},{"time":625000,"text":"and actually start decrypting it."},{"time":627000,"text":"Well the yellow part of the code is now decrypted."},{"time":629000,"text":"And I know, it doesn't really look much different from the original."},{"time":632000,"text":"But just keep staring at it."},{"time":634000,"text":"You'll actually see that down here"},{"time":636000,"text":"you can see a Web address:"},{"time":638000,"text":"unionseek.com/d/ioo.exe"},{"time":644000,"text":"And when you view this image on your computer"},{"time":646000,"text":"it actually is going to download and run that program."},{"time":648000,"text":"And that's a backdoor which will take over your computer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":651000,"text":"But even more interestingly,"},{"time":653000,"text":"if we continue decrypting,"},{"time":655000,"text":"we'll find this mysterious string,"},{"time":657000,"text":"which says O600KO78RUS."},{"time":662000,"text":"That code is there underneath the encryption"},{"time":664000,"text":"as some sort of a signature."},{"time":666000,"text":"It's not used for anything."},{"time":668000,"text":"And I was looking at that, trying to figure out what it means."},{"time":671000,"text":"So obviously I Googled for it."},{"time":673000,"text":"I got zero hits; wasn't there."},{"time":675000,"text":"So I spoke with the guys at the lab."},{"time":677000,"text":"And we have a couple of Russian guys in our labs,"},{"time":679000,"text":"and one of them mentioned,"},{"time":681000,"text":"well, it ends in RUS like Russia."},{"time":683000,"text":"And 78 is the city code"},{"time":685000,"text":"for the city of St. Petersburg."},{"time":687000,"text":"For example, you can find it from some phone numbers"},{"time":689000,"text":"and car license plates and stuff like that."},{"time":692000,"text":"So I went looking for contacts in St. Petersburg,"},{"time":695000,"text":"and through a long road,"},{"time":697000,"text":"we eventually found this one particular website."}]},{"cues":[{"time":701000,"text":"Here's this Russian guy who's been operating online for a number of years"},{"time":704000,"text":"who runs his own website,"},{"time":706000,"text":"and he runs a blog under the popular Live Journal."},{"time":709000,"text":"And on this blog, he blogs about his life,"},{"time":711000,"text":"about his life in St. Petersburg --"},{"time":713000,"text":"he's in his early 20s --"},{"time":715000,"text":"about his cat,"},{"time":717000,"text":"about his girlfriend."},{"time":719000,"text":"And he drives a very nice car."},{"time":721000,"text":"In fact, this guy drives"},{"time":724000,"text":"a Mercedes-Benz S600"},{"time":726000,"text":"V12"},{"time":728000,"text":"with a six-liter engine"},{"time":730000,"text":"with more than 400 horsepower."},{"time":732000,"text":"Now that's a nice car for a 20-something year-old kid in St. Petersburg."}]},{"cues":[{"time":736000,"text":"How do I know about this car?"},{"time":738000,"text":"Because he blogged about the car."},{"time":740000,"text":"He actually had a car accident."},{"time":742000,"text":"In downtown St. Petersburg,"},{"time":744000,"text":"he actually crashed his car into another car."},{"time":746000,"text":"And he put blogged images about the car accident --"},{"time":748000,"text":"that's his Mercedes --"},{"time":750000,"text":"right here is the Lada Samara he crashed into."},{"time":754000,"text":"And you can actually see that the license plate of the Samara"},{"time":757000,"text":"ends in 78RUS."},{"time":759000,"text":"And if you actually take a look at the scene picture,"},{"time":762000,"text":"you can see that the plate of the Mercedes"},{"time":764000,"text":"is O600KO78RUS."},{"time":770000,"text":"Now I'm not a lawyer,"},{"time":772000,"text":"but if I would be,"},{"time":774000,"text":"this is where I would say, \"I rest my case.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":777000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":779000,"text":"So what happens when online criminals are caught?"},{"time":782000,"text":"Well in most cases it never gets this far."},{"time":785000,"text":"The vast majority of the online crime cases,"},{"time":787000,"text":"we don't even know which continent the attacks are coming from."},{"time":790000,"text":"And even if we are able to find online criminals,"},{"time":793000,"text":"quite often there is no outcome."},{"time":795000,"text":"The local police don't act, or if they do, there's not enough evidence,"},{"time":798000,"text":"or for some reason we can't take them down."},{"time":800000,"text":"I wish it would be easier;"},{"time":802000,"text":"unfortunately it isn't."}]},{"cues":[{"time":804000,"text":"But things are also changing"},{"time":807000,"text":"at a very rapid pace."},{"time":810000,"text":"You've all heard about things like Stuxnet."},{"time":813000,"text":"So if you look at what Stuxnet did"},{"time":816000,"text":"is that it infected these."},{"time":818000,"text":"That's a Siemens S7-400 PLC,"},{"time":821000,"text":"programmable logic [controller]."},{"time":823000,"text":"And this is what runs our infrastructure."},{"time":826000,"text":"This is what runs everything around us."},{"time":829000,"text":"PLC's, these small boxes which have no display,"},{"time":832000,"text":"no keyboard,"},{"time":834000,"text":"which are programmed, are put in place, and they do their job."},{"time":836000,"text":"For example, the elevators in this building"},{"time":838000,"text":"most likely are controlled by one of these."},{"time":842000,"text":"And when Stuxnet infects one of these,"},{"time":845000,"text":"that's a massive revolution"},{"time":847000,"text":"on the kinds of risks we have to worry about."},{"time":850000,"text":"Because everything around us is being run by these."},{"time":853000,"text":"I mean, we have critical infrastructure."},{"time":855000,"text":"You go to any factory, any power plant,"},{"time":858000,"text":"any chemical plant, any food processing plant,"},{"time":860000,"text":"you look around --"},{"time":862000,"text":"everything is being run by computers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":864000,"text":"Everything is being run by computers."},{"time":866000,"text":"Everything is reliant on these computers working."},{"time":869000,"text":"We have become very reliant"},{"time":872000,"text":"on Internet,"},{"time":874000,"text":"on basic things like electricity, obviously,"},{"time":877000,"text":"on computers working."},{"time":879000,"text":"And this really is something"},{"time":881000,"text":"which creates completely new problems for us."},{"time":883000,"text":"We must have some way"},{"time":885000,"text":"of continuing to work"},{"time":887000,"text":"even if computers fail."}]},{"cues":[{"time":897000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":899000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":909000,"text":"So preparedness means that we can do stuff"},{"time":912000,"text":"even when the things we take for granted"},{"time":914000,"text":"aren't there."},{"time":916000,"text":"It's actually very basic stuff --"},{"time":918000,"text":"thinking about continuity, thinking about backups,"},{"time":921000,"text":"thinking about the things that actually matter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":924000,"text":"Now I told you --"},{"time":927000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":929000,"text":"I love the Internet. I do."},{"time":933000,"text":"Think about all the services we have online."},{"time":936000,"text":"Think about if they are taken away from you,"},{"time":939000,"text":"if one day you don't actually have them"},{"time":941000,"text":"for some reason or another."},{"time":943000,"text":"I see beauty in the future of the Internet,"},{"time":946000,"text":"but I'm worried"},{"time":948000,"text":"that we might not see that."},{"time":950000,"text":"I'm worried that we are running into problems"},{"time":952000,"text":"because of online crime."},{"time":954000,"text":"Online crime is the one thing"},{"time":956000,"text":"that might take these things away from us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":958000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":961000,"text":"I've spent my life"},{"time":963000,"text":"defending the Net,"},{"time":966000,"text":"and I do feel that if we don't fight online crime,"},{"time":969000,"text":"we are running a risk of losing it all."},{"time":973000,"text":"We have to do this globally,"},{"time":976000,"text":"and we have to do it right now."},{"time":979000,"text":"What we need"},{"time":981000,"text":"is more global, international law enforcement work"},{"time":984000,"text":"to find online criminal gangs --"},{"time":986000,"text":"these organized gangs"},{"time":988000,"text":"that are making millions out of their attacks."},{"time":990000,"text":"That's much more important"},{"time":992000,"text":"than running anti-viruses or running firewalls."},{"time":994000,"text":"What actually matters"},{"time":996000,"text":"is actually finding the people behind these attacks,"},{"time":998000,"text":"and even more importantly,"},{"time":1000000,"text":"we have to find the people"},{"time":1002000,"text":"who are about to become"},{"time":1004000,"text":"part of this online world of crime,"},{"time":1006000,"text":"but haven't yet done it."},{"time":1008000,"text":"We have to find the people with the skills,"},{"time":1011000,"text":"but without the opportunities"},{"time":1013000,"text":"and give them the opportunities"},{"time":1015000,"text":"to use their skills for good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1018000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1020000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}